{"tid":1541831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"重點係人道同人權！","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T16:33:59.000Z","uid":91666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0454bfdade6a2baf7b3d74726349f41e259520e","tid":1541831,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"請大家集中返視點，其實各國代表都係集中晌人道呢個議題！<br />\n<br />\n手捉被打到無反應；傷者被強行延遲救援；被捕人仕被阻攔尋求法律支援；被捕人仕受到多番虐打/凌辱等...<br />\n我諗各國比我地更清楚中國/佢管治既地方擁有幾多人道.而各國傳媒都多次報到香港示威係好和平.<br />\n<br />\n今日沒收物資，聽日可以收你車/屋/任何資產！<br />\n今日上得巴士入得地鐵打人趕走FA&amp;記者，聽日可以上黎你屋企要你簽/承認/做任何野.<br />\n<br />\n請大家加大力度比所有人知跟幾日呢個國際城市既市民面對緊乜野.<br />\n公佈出黎已經過千手足被剝奪佢地既生活/公民權利/生存權利等...無人知係可以係幾何級數上.<br />\n<br />\n既然能夠動議撤回可以令一部份人認為係勝利，代表以往我地太過著眼表達反送中！<br />\n<br />\n懇求大家正視問題核心，一起堅持！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"14c7161fd4187dc822adb68e9d5d62e2a1eb6e13","tid":1541831,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【Google 廣告】上線啦</span> !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dOiPeS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dOiPeS</a>"},{"pid":"72d7718447b4ddcbc1a56378c08ab4237f087838","tid":1541831,"uid":245841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:19:51.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!!!<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！"},{"pid":"1c864b9fdb10e42bd86780781378c1d4fe5b314f","tid":1541831,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be099ab13ae91942a519848b9ffe34667651ecc3","tid":1541831,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote><em>我們成長為自由人。 沒人可讓一個自由的人下跪。<br />\nWe grew up as free people. No one can make a free person kneel.</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>《HONG KONG BE WATER》</strong></span></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、<span style=\"color: violet;\">民主人權法案</span>、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債 主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n提防 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美、德領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天